Marka, waxaan tixraac karnaa daraasadihii hore ee ku saabsan cudurada kale ee Corona, gaar ahaan SARS-CoV, iyo MERS-CoV (Sawirro (Sawirro 4) 4).
Guud ahaan, ka dib markii fayras uu ku soo duulo martida, nidaamka difaaca jirka ee caadiga ah wuxuu aqoonsan yahay iyada oo loo marayo soo-dhoweeyayaasha aqoonsiga qaababka (PRRS) oo ay ku jiraan soo-dhoweeyayaasha nooca C ee u eg, soo-dhoweeyayaasha u eg tol (TLR), soo-dhoweeyayaasha u eg baaxadda qaybaha isku xidhka nukliyeerada (NLR), iyo soo-dhoweeyayaasha u eg borotiinka RIG-I (RLR).
Wadooyin kala duwan, fayrasku wuxuu kiciyaa soo ifbaxida caabuqa, bislaanshaha unugyada, iyo sameynta interferons nooca I (IFN) oo xaddidaya faafitaanka fayraska iyo dardargelinta unugyada weyn ee fayraska ee antibodies-ka.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, borotiinka N ee SARS-CoV wuxuu ka caawin karaa fayraska inuu ka baxsado jawaabta difaaca jirka.
jawaabta difaaca jirka ee la qabsiga ah ayaa si dhakhso ah ugu biireysa dagaalka ka dhanka ah fayraska.
Unugyada T-ka ee lymphocyte-ka ah, oo ay ku jiraan unugyada CD4+ iyo CD8+ T, waxay door muhiim ah ka ciyaaraan difaaca.
Unugyada CD4+ waxay kiciyaan unugyada B inay soo saaraan unugyada difaaca ee loo qoondeeyay fayraska, unugyada CD8+ waxay si toos ah u dilaan unugyada fayraska qaba.
