asalka xayawaanka ee fayraska loo yaqaan 'Human coronaviruses'
Isbedelka iyo la qabsiga ayaa horseeday isbedelka wadajirka ah ee fayraska corona iyo dadka ay ku nool yihiin, oo ay ku jiraan dadka, kumanaan sano ka hor.
Sanadkii 2003 ka hor, waxaa la ogaa in laba nooc oo ah cudurka loo yaqaan 'Human coronaviruses' ay keenaan cudurro fudud sida hargabka.
Cudurka neefsashada ee daran ee SARS iyo MERS ayaa muujiyey wajiga kale si loo muujiyo sida ay u daran tahay iyo halista nolosha ee cudurka loo yaqaan 'Human coronaviruses'.
