Bali waxaa lagu soo warramey inay tahay meesha ugu yar ee ay awoodaan in ka badan 20 meelood oo caan ah marka loo eego diyaarinta, halka magaalooyinka Australia ay u muuqdaan kuwo aad u awooda badan. Australia waxay soo saartay qorshaheeda jawaabta degdegga ah ee cudurka cusub ee Coronavirus (COVID-19) 7 Febraayo.
