ACE2 waxay ku xidhan tahay dusha sare ee unugyada sanbabada, xididdada wadnaha, kelyaha iyo sidoo kale mindhicirka.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 wuxuu ka hortagaa shaqada angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE) isagoo yareynaya xaddiga angiotensin 2 iyo kordhinta angiotensin (1-7); taas oo ka dhigaysa daawo rajo leh oo lagu daaweynayo cudurada wadnaha iyo dhiigga.
Nooca bini'aadamka ee enzyme-ka waxaa badanaa loo yaqaan hACE2.
Enzyme-ka loo yaqaan 'angiotensin-converting enzyme 2' waa enzyme bir ah oo zinc ku jira, waxaana ku yaal dusha unugyada gudaha iyo unugyada kale.
Badeecadaas waxay leedahay M2 peptidase oo leh amino-dhameystiran, iyo silsilad-collectin-carboxyl-dhameystiran oo ah gaadiidka amino-acids-ka kelyaha.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 waa borotiinka uniprotic-ka ee nooca 1 ee leh soo-dhoweeyeyaasha firfircoon ee ku yaal dusha unugyada sanbabada iyo unugyada kale.
Qaybta ka baxsan xadka unugyada ee angiotensin-2 waxaa ka go'da xadka dhexdhexaadka ah ee unugyada by enzymes loo yaqaan shidases taasina waxay keentaa in borotiinka lagu milmi karo uu dhiiga galo ka dibna uu ka baxo kaadida.
Enzyma-ga ee loo yaqaan 'angiotensin-2' waxaa laga helaa xubnaha badankood: wuxuu ku xidhan yahay xuubka unugyada nooca 2 ee sanbabada, unugyada xiidmaha yaryar, unugyada xiidmaha ee xididdada iyo xididdada, iyo sidoo kale unugyada muruqyada ee darbiga wadnaha ku jira xubnaha badankood.
RNA-ga oo ah wakiilka loo yaqaan 'angiotensin-2' waxaa lagu helaa maskaxda, qanjirka, hooska iyo jirka.
Shaqada ugu weyn ee angiotensin-2 waa inay u shaqeyso sidii dheelitirka angiotensin-transferase.
Enzyma-ka angiotensin-ka ayaa kiciya in hormoonka angiotensin 1 loo beddelo angiotensin 2 oo ah hormoonka xidha xididdada dhiigga.
Dhinaca kale, enzyme-ka loo yaqaan 'angiotensin-2' wuxuu ka soo saaraa dhinaca carboxyl ee ku jira amino acid-ka phenylalanine ee angio-tensin 2 (aspartate-arginine-valine-tyrosine-isoleucine-histidine-brolin-phenylalanine) wuxuuna u kala saaraa inuu u bedelo angio-tensin (1-7), (histidine-aspartate-arginine-valine-tyrosine-isoleucine-histidine-brolin-phenylalanine).
Enzyme-ka angiotacin 2 wuxuu u kala qaybiyaa dhowr peptides oo kale oo ay ka mid yihiin [des-arginine9] - bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A, iyo gerlin.
Enzyme-ka loo yaqaan 'angiotensin-transferase 2' wuxuu sidoo kale nidaamiyaa gaadiidka dhexdhexaadka ah ee loo yaqaan 'SLC6A19' oo ah nooca loo yaqaan 'neutral transporter' oo ah amino acid-ka isku midka ah, wuxuuna door ka ciyaaraa cudurka 'Hartens' syndrome'.
Enzyme-transferase angiotensin 2, oo ah borotiinka dhexdhexaadka ah, waa gelitaanka ugu weyn ee unugyada qaar ka mid ah fayraska corona, oo ay ku jiraan HRV NL63, SARS-CoV (virus-ka sababa SARS), iyo SARS-CoV-2 (virus-ka sababa cudurka COVID-19).
Gaar ahaan, isku xirnaanta borotiinka S1 ee SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV-2 ee heerka enzymatic ee angiotensin-2 ee dusha sare ee unugyada waxay keentaa in unugyada ay is-dhexgalaan, fayraska iyo enzyme-ka ay u gudbaan unugyada gudaha.
Nidaamkan gelitaanka wuxuu u baahan yahay in borotiinka S uu ku soo baxo enzyme-ka protease-ka ee ka dhex jira xuubka, Serin2 ee martida, kaas oo weli la tijaabinayo daaweyn ahaan. Tani waxay keentay in qaar ay u maleynayaan in hoos u dhigista heerarka enzyme-ka loo yaqaan 'angiotensin-2' ee unugyada ay ka caawin karto difaacidda cudurka.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, ururo badan oo takhasus leh iyo hay'ado is-xakamaynaya ayaa ku talinaya in la sii wado isticmaalka daaweynta caadiga ah ee angio-transferase inhibitors iyo angio-receptor blockers.
Daraasad nidaamsan iyo falanqayn la sameeyay oo la daabacay July 11, 2012 ayaa muujisay in "isticmaalka angiotensin-converting enzyme inhibitors ay la socdeen hoos u dhac muuqda oo ah khatarta sambabada 34% marka loo eego kooxda tixraaca".
Intaa waxaa dheer, "qiyaasta sambabada ayaa hoos u dhacday dadka la daaweeyay angiotensin-converting enzyme inhibitors, kuwaas oo ay ka badan tahay inay qabaan sambabada, gaar ahaan kuwa qaba wadnaha ama wadnaha oo daciif ah.
Isticmaalka angiotensin-transferase inhibitors waxay hoos u dhigtay dhimashada sambabada, inkastoo natiijooyinku ay ka hooseeyeen halista guud ee sambabada".
Waxaa la rumeysan yahay in enzyme-ka loo yaqaan 'human angiotensin converting enzyme 2' (rhACE2) uu noqon doono daaweyn cusub oo loogu talagalay dhaawacyada sanbabada ee daran, waxaana la ogaaday inuu hagaajiyo wareegga dhiigga sanbabada, iyo sidoo kale oksijiinta ee doofaarka qaba cudurka neef-mareenka ee badan ee dufanka leh.
Nolosha nuska ah ee angiotensin-2 waxaa lagu qiyaasaa 10 saacadood, waxayna bilaabataa 30 daqiiqo kadib, waxayna sii soconaysaa 24 saacadood.
Waxaa jira caddayn badan oo muujinaya in angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 ay noqon karto daaweyn rajo leh dadka aan u dulqaadan karin daawooyinka caadiga ah ee angiotensin-converting enzyme (RAS) iyo cudurada ay la socdaan kororka dhiigga ee angiotensin-converting enzyme 2. Waxaa jira tijaabooyin caafimaad oo la qiimeynayo oo ku saabsan saameynta ay leedahay in lagu buufiyo angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 ee daaweynta xanuunka neef-mareenka ee daran.
Codsiyada COVID-19 waa barnaamijyo barnaamijyo ah oo loogu talagalay qalabka gacanta si gaar ah loogu talagalay in lagu caawiyo raadraaca dadka la xiriiray ee ka jawaabaya cudurka faafa ee Coronavirus ee 2019-20, taas oo macnaheedu yahay in la aqoonsado dadka ("la xiriiray") ee la xiriiray qof uu cudurka qabo.
Codsiyo badan ayaa la sameeyay ama la soo jeediyay iyadoo ay taageero rasmi ah ka heleyso dowlada gobollada iyo maamullada qaarkood.
Waxaa jira qaab dhismeedyo badan oo lagu dhisayo codsiyada raadraaca xiriirka.
Dad badan ayaa ka walaacsan asturnaanta, gaar ahaan nidaamyada ku saleysan raadraaca goobta dadka isticmaala barnaamijyada.
Beddellada aan ku xadgudbin asturnaanta waxaa ka mid ah isticmaalka calaamadaha Bluetooth si loo diiwaangeliyo u dhowrista isticmaalaha taleefannada kale ee gacanta.
Bishii Abriil 10, 2020, Google iyo Apple waxay wadajir ku dhawaaqeen inay ku darsadeen shaqo taageereysa barnaamijyadaas ku saleysan Bluetooth, si toos ah nidaamyadooda hawlgalka ee Android iyo iOS.
Shiinaha, dowladda Shiinaha oo kaashanaysa Alipay ayaa soo saartay barnaamij u oggolaanaya muwaadiniinta inay hubiyaan inay la xiriireen dadka qaba COVID-19.
waa barnaamij ay dadka isticmaalaan in ka badan 200 magaalo oo Shiinaha ah. Singapore, dadka waxay isticmaalaan barnaamij la yiraahdo TraceTogether.
Urur ka tirsan bulshada IT-ga ayaa sameeyay naqshadeynta barnaamijka, waxaana loo sii daayay barnaamij furan oo la doonayo in la siiyo dowladda. Waqooyiga Macedonia ayaa soo saartay barnaamijka "StopKorona", oo ah barnaamij ku saleysan Bluetooth oo lagu raad raaco soo-gaadhista dadka qaba cudurka iyo in si deg deg ah looga jawaabo saraakiisha daryeelka caafimaadka.
Wasaaradda Isgaarsiinta iyo Teknolojiyada ayaa la shaqeysay Wasaaradda Caafimaadka si ay u sameeyaan barnaamijka.
Bishii Abriil 14, 2020, barnaamijku wuxuu weli sugayay ansixinta dukaanka Google Play iyo App Store ee Apple.
Bishii Abriil 12, dowladda ayaa sheegtay in barnaamijka raadraaca xiriirka uu ku jiro marxaladda horumarinta sare, waxaana laga yaabaa inuu diyaar u noqdo qaybinta toddobaadyo gudahood. Ireland iyo Faransiiska ayaa qorsheynaya inay bilaabaan barnaamij la mid ah, oo ah "StopCovid".
Australia iyo New Zealand waxay ka fekereen inay sameeyaan barnaamijyo ku saleysan barnaamijka TraceTogether ee Singapore, iyo sidoo kale BlueTree.Tree.Russia waxay qorsheyneysaa inay soo bandhigto barnaamij u adeegsanaya jawiga muuqaalka ah ee bukaannada laga helay COVID-19 ee deggan Moscow, kaas oo loogu talagalay in lagu hubiyo inaysan ka bixin guryahooda.
Ross Anderson oo ah borofisar ku takhasusay injineernimada amniga ee jaamacadda Cambridge ayaa sheegay dhibaatooyin badan oo ku saabsan nidaamyada ku saleysan codsiyada, oo ay ku jiraan kiisaska been abuurka ah iyo waxtar la'aanta suurtagalka ah haddii codsiyada loo isticmaalo dadka yar.
Si wax looga qabto walaaca ku saabsan faafitaanka barnaamijyada khalkhalgelinta ama waxyeelada leh ee loo yaqaan 'coronavirus', Apple waxay xaddiday noocyada ururada ay ku dari karaan barnaamijyada ay la xiriiraan coronavirus-ka dukaankooda; waxay ku xaddiday kaliya ururada "rasmiga ah" ama kuwa kale ee sumcad leh.
Google iyo Amazon waxay sameeyeen xaddidaadyo la mid ah.
Dadka u dooda asturnaanta waxay muujiyeen walaac ku saabsan saameynta ay yeelan karto adeegsiga barnaamijyada kormeerka ee loo yaqaan 'coronavirus apps', gaar ahaan haddii kaabayaasha kormeerka ee loogu talagalay in lagu maareeyo cudurka faafa ee loo yaqaan 'coronavirus pandemic' ay baabi'i doonaan marka khatarta ay dhammaato.
Ururka cafis caalamiga ah iyo in ka badan 100 urur oo kale ayaa soo saaray bayaan ay ugu baaqeen in la xakameeyo noocan oo kale ah kormeerka.
Ururada ayaa sidoo kale ku dhawaaqay sideed shuruud oo loogu talagalay mashaariicda dowladda:
kormeerka waa inuu ahaadaa mid "sharci ah, lagama maarmaan ah, iyo mid ku habboon";
kordhinta kormeerka iyo kormeerka waa inay ku jiraan qodobo ku saabsan go'aaminta waqtiga ay joojinayaan;
isticmaalka xogta waa in lagu xaddidaa ujeeddooyinka la xiriira COVID-19;
Amniga xogta iyo sirta aqoonsiga dadka haysta waa in la ilaaliyaa, oo la xaqiijiyaa in la ilaaliyo caddaynta;
Kormeerka dhijitaalka ah waa inuu ka fogaadaa takoorka iyo ka-goynta;
la wadaagida xogta dhinacyada kale waa in lagu qeexaa sharciga;
Waa in la helaa ilaalin ka hortagga xadgudubka iyo ilaalinta xuquuqda muwaadiniinta si looga hortago xadgudubyada;
"Ka qaybgalka wax ku oolka ah" ee dhammaan "dhaqdhaqaaqayaasha la xiriira" ayaa loo baahan yahay, oo ay ku jiraan khubarada caafimaadka dadweynaha iyo kooxaha laga reebay. Jamhuuriyadda Jarmalka ee Chaos Computer Club (CCC) iyo Reporters Without Borders (RSF) ayaa sidoo kale soo saaray liisaska dib u eegista.
Qorshaha la soo jeediyay ee Google/Apple wuxuu ujeedadiisu tahay in wax laga qabto dhibaatada la socodka joogtada ah iyadoo laga saaro raadraaca nidaamyada qalabka marka loo baahdo.
Wadamada qaar waxay isticmaalaan raadraaca goobta ee shabakada ah halkii ay ka isticmaali lahaayeen barnaamijyada, taas oo baabi'ineysa baahida loo qabo in la soo dejiyo barnaamijka waxayna bixisaa fursad looga fogaado raadraaca.
